{"id": "cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling__a2-late-chunking__0002", "text": "[Cybersecurity](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/veilig/index.html)", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling__a2-late-chunking__0002", "source_slug": "cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling", "source_title": "Cyber ​​security decision and physical resilience: legislation ready for consideration", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling.html", "source_date": "2025-08-18", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 2, "n_chunks_total": 13, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 2}}
{"id": "cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling__a2-late-chunking__0003", "text": "The draft versions of the Cyber Security Decree and the Resilience of Critical Entities Decree (WKE) are now with the House of Representatives. This represents a next step in strengthening the digital and physical security of vital sectors.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling__a2-late-chunking__0003", "source_slug": "cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling", "source_title": "Cyber ​​security decision and physical resilience: legislation ready for consideration", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling.html", "source_date": "2025-08-18", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 3, "n_chunks_total": 13, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 3}}
{"id": "cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling__a2-late-chunking__0004", "text": "Many more sectors will soon be supervised under NIS2, such as energy, healthcare, transport, finance and digital infrastructure. Organizations will be given stricter obligations in terms of risk assessment, incident reporting and recovery measures.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling__a2-late-chunking__0004", "source_slug": "cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling", "source_title": "Cyber ​​security decision and physical resilience: legislation ready for consideration", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling.html", "source_date": "2025-08-18", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 4, "n_chunks_total": 13, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 4}}
{"id": "cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling__a2-late-chunking__0005", "text": "The WKE decision obliges vital organizations to protect themselves against physical disasters such as sabotage or natural disasters. Careful risk analyzes and preventive measures are becoming the norm.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling__a2-late-chunking__0005", "source_slug": "cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling", "source_title": "Cyber ​​security decision and physical resilience: legislation ready for consideration", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling.html", "source_date": "2025-08-18", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 5, "n_chunks_total": 13, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 5}}
{"id": "cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling__a2-late-chunking__0006", "text": "The decisions were reached after extensive consultation. The legal texts are clear and enforceable, with clear definitions and demarcations. Now we have to wait for quick political approval.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling__a2-late-chunking__0006", "source_slug": "cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling", "source_title": "Cyber ​​security decision and physical resilience: legislation ready for consideration", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling.html", "source_date": "2025-08-18", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 6, "n_chunks_total": 13, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 6}}
{"id": "cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling__a2-late-chunking__0007", "text": "View the official documents of the [House of Representatives](https://www.tweedekamer.nl/kamerstuks/brief_administratie/detail?id=2025Z13678&did=2025D31013).", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling__a2-late-chunking__0007", "source_slug": "cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling", "source_title": "Cyber ​​security decision and physical resilience: legislation ready for consideration", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling.html", "source_date": "2025-08-18", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 7, "n_chunks_total": 13, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 7}}
{"id": "cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling__a2-late-chunking__0008", "text": "About 1 in 5 entrepreneurs is confronted with cybercrime. Such a cyber incident can have major consequences for business operations, customers, suppliers or reputation. Taking appropriate measures is therefore important for every company.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling__a2-late-chunking__0008", "source_slug": "cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling", "source_title": "Cyber ​​security decision and physical resilience: legislation ready for consideration", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling.html", "source_date": "2025-08-18", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 8, "n_chunks_total": 13, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 8}}
{"id": "cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling__a2-late-chunking__0009", "text": "- Do you have an SME company and do you want to reduce your cyber risks? Then take a look at [Cyber ​​Fundament](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/cyber-voor-het-mkb/), especially for SME entrepreneurs.\n- Learn more about the 4-in-1 cyber solution [Cyber ​​Safe & Secure](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/cyber-veilig-en-zeker/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link) especially for large businesses and reduce your cyber risks.\n- Do you also want to [do business safely](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/veilig-ondernemen/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link)? View smart tools, useful articles and cyber webinars.\n- [Report fraud to us](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/prive/abnamro/veilig-banken/fraude-melden.html \"Report fraud\"), even if in doubt, after which our helpdesk will help you immediately.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling__a2-late-chunking__0009", "source_slug": "cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling", "source_title": "Cyber ​​security decision and physical resilience: legislation ready for consideration", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/cyberbeveiligingsbesluit-en-fysieke-weerbaarheid-wetgeving-klaar-voor-behandeling.html", "source_date": "2025-08-18", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 9, "n_chunks_total": 13, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 9}}
